{"tid":1825672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【陳同佳案】台灣擬提供150萬補償金 給潘曉穎家屬","createTime":"2020-01-15T13:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T13:38:56.000Z","uid":209657,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d66cdcc704ddb07a08ac783aeb8d5fd75be48e44","tid":1825672,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:16:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.pts.org.tw/article/462733\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.pts.org.tw%2Farticle%2F462733&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=fc3d4b76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.pts.org.tw/article/462733</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人陳同佳涉嫌在台灣殺害女友潘小姐，我國有意提供150萬元補償金給受害者家屬，陸委會指出，已經透過駐港處聯絡潘曉穎的家人申請。至於陳同佳依然沒有來台投案，陸委會表示「遺憾」，呼籲港府負起責任。<br />\n<br />\n2018年2月，香港男子陳同佳涉嫌在台旅遊期間殺害女友潘曉穎，事後棄屍、潛逃回香港。依據《犯罪被害人保護法》規定，在中華民國的領域內因犯罪行為被害死亡，遺屬可申請補償金，不分國籍。所以陸委會已透過駐港處，聯絡潘曉穎的家人可依台灣法律申請150萬元補償。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會副主委邱垂正表示，「我們也透過我們駐香港的台北文化經濟辦事處，聯絡這個案子的被害者潘姓女子的家屬，相關的程序都在處理當中，我們是提醒他。」<br />\n<br />\n陸委會指出如果潘女的家屬申請，我國就會依法受理。而陳同佳來台投案有進展嗎？陸委會說已成立專案窗口，但仍未獲港方或陳同佳任何聯繫。邱垂正說，「截至目前為止，陳同佳還沒有向投案窗口來聯繫，對於這個事情我們感到遺憾。」<br />\n<br />\n司法互助沒有進展，港媒則引述消息人士認為港府在此案一直處於下風，而且也欠缺熟悉台灣事務的專家，加上台灣處理手法政治化，兩地移送陳同佳的方式沒有共識，預料短期之內難有進展。"},{"pid":"8b6467f436e0c46b2e2455c8667368e2075fcc9b","tid":1825672,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:22:45.000Z","msg":"1.19 立即民主政改 否則天下制裁 大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1825673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1825673</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8f7ab1c12c155b0b07148c2d7dd462efea993180","tid":1825672,"uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:22:46.000Z","msg":"陸委會今日表示，潘女家屬如提出申請，政府會依法受理，希望能稍撫慰家屬心靈。<br />\n<br />\nDklm藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0301ebc87249d59d7a779bcb709a2ec4b4d25ab","tid":1825672,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"台灣陸委會港澳處長杜嘉芬表示，據知陳同佳仍住在安全屋<br />\n係咪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee34667188890ac31c3f7d99ce195ff6442d4ee2","tid":1825672,"uid":150675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"又打左港府一巴 台灣no.1!!!"},{"pid":"147a2537c9ef81edc5b3334a6a3f56790e83ecc3","tid":1825672,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"150萬台幣<br />\n已經落鳩港共臉<br />\n抵畀<br />\n<br />\n林鄭搓心呢"},{"pid":"391033617a4a3f4b513c1364685609f5b3f44b1f","tid":1825672,"uid":69157,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:27:19.000Z","msg":"一個畀大陸話勒緊褲頭嘅地方竟然都會識得體卹死者家屬"},{"pid":"fdf9d24edca380808822bf0d4a0c2056004fbd5e","tid":1825672,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"391033617a4a3f4b513c1364685609f5b3f44b1f","tid":1825672,"uid":69157,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:27:19.000Z","msg":"一個畀大陸話勒緊褲頭嘅地方竟然都會識得體卹死者家屬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d870ede20ca2b2fe56d7d6a953dc796b33ef897","tid":1825672,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"147a2537c9ef81edc5b3334a6a3f56790e83ecc3","tid":1825672,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"150萬台幣<br />